race.description: Become A Brc Member Qtis 2YO Maiden Plate
race.comment: The babies kick us off with a few of these facing the starter for the first time. The well-related HARRY'S MODE (3) (half to Listed winner Scenic Point) is on debut but has shown ability at the trials and gets some weight relief with the claim. Only needs some luck from the wide draw to be playing a role in the outcome. AREPRICE (1) is another at the races for the first time but looked handy in a recent Eagle Farm trial and can run a race first-up. CINCHICATED (6) is sure to be well-educated out of the Kendrick barn and should be kept very safe. I'LLTELLYOUANYTIME (8) next in line with race experience on her side.
